Abstract Factory
================

[1] As the name suggests it is the "family of factories":
    "Family of products" and corresponding "famliy of factories" which uses
    inheritence to actually allows you to polymorphically call on different
    factories.

[2] HotDrink.hpp:
    It has different Products

[3] HotDrinkFactory.hpp:
    It has Abastract Factory and derived Factories corresponding to the
    Products (HotDrink.hpp)

[4] DrinkFactory.hpp
    - It is going to be the concrete implementation of Abstarct Factory.

[5] main.cpp


